data.description: ADVENTURE AWAITS THIS RARE FIND!!! THAT WILL NOT LAST LONG!! This 1.5 Acre PENINSULA PROPERTY captures timeless true southern river living. Situated on Perch creek with two points of access to Dog River. No doubt this home was set up for indoor and outdoor entertaining!  An Expansive brick paver patio with tranquil water view is the perfect place for that morning cup of coffee or an afternoon WINE DOWN! Oversized sparking pool is perfect for those hot summer days. Side entry of home features covered parking and exterior storage room. This entry takes you directly into the mudroom providing ease for unloading the day. The homes design was carefully planned out to maximize water views from almost every room. The bold double door entry leads you into the foyer of the home setting the tone of traditional dedicated spaces with an open floor plan feel! The galley style kitchen maximizes function and is complete with plenty of counter prep space and cabinet storage. Just off the kitchen is a flex space that is currently being used as an office. This cozy space offers serene water views and is perfect for those who work from home! Adjacent is the dual-purpose working zone acting as a laundry and mudroom. The living room has rich wood flooring and is anchored with a brick wall wood burning fireplace. This space is also adorned with a floor to ceiling six-panel curved window that allows the warm sunshine to flow throughout.  The living room flows directly into the formal dining allowing this space to take advantage of the sunlight and dining by the fire. The informal dining has a double sliding door that leads you to an outdoor oasis. The guest bedrooms are super spacious with one having access to the outdoor patio. The master bedroom has a dual closet the spans the length of the room with a dedicated en suite. The adjacent property with large workshop is currently not for sale but will be put on the market this year for anyone looking for two properties side by side.  Don't miss the opportunity to live the river life and let nature serenade you day and night!!      BUYER AND BUYER'S AGENT TO VERIFY ALL INFORMATION DEEMED IMPORTANT
